Spotify needs to add a shuffle queue option. I add a bunch of albums that match my mood to the queue but they play in order and if you want to bounce between different artist, you would have to manually select the placement of each song. There's no time for that and I like the surprise of shuffle. Also Spotify could use a better variety in their artist radios. I find the most mainstream songs out today in every artist radio I peek at. Even though most these artist are categorized under the genres of Hip-Hop & R&B, Spotify should recognize there are many styles, like subgenres, under this category. For an example, I don't think Young Thug or 21 savage belong in 6lack radio. As for the positives of Spotify, they do have customized radios for you to explore new music. I enjoy the Daily Mix stations especially, it plays music from your library and similar songs that aren't but maybe should be. Also the Release Radar station is a good go-to to hear nothing but new releases, catered around your music preferences. This is my thoughts of the 3 month trial I am using.. I'll need the shuffle option for my queue to continue using Spotify as my primary music platform. I can see why it is the top pick, since Apple & Play users can both use it. I think anyone who is as passionate about new music as much as me can relate. Please Hear me out & I'll rewrite this into a 5 star review!!

Exploring out of my comfort zone is as easy a button press.  If I had to find a con, is it changes layout right as I'm very comfortable with the previous one. I'd call it a minor con, because it's so we'll designed.   Even with ads, the app still shines brighter than it's competitors. However, I find the differences between music apps is personal preference. I feel like Spotify has it going for just ease of use and astheticly pleasing.  Highly suggest you try the free trial to get a full featured experience.

まずTwitterには無い点を挙げる ・画像をタップせずとも横にスクロール出来る。これは漫画作品や動画、イラストの投稿の仕方に多様性をもたらす ・1〜10個の画像及び動画を投稿出来る ・文字制限無し 次に悪い点を挙げる ・写真や動画を投稿する時の選択画面を今すぐ直すべき。アルバムの指定が出来ず、1万枚の写真があったとしたら、その中から1〜10枚を選ばなければならない。苦行である ・DM、ハッシュタグ、ストーリー等Instagramにある機能が搭載されていない。これではただのインスタの付属品 ・投稿された画像のDL保存は出来ない ・UIも分かりにくい そして、Twitter対抗の為に必要な課題と展望を述べる ・metaは、ThreadsをFacebookとInstagramの融合体にして既存SNSの完全上位互換の発展型とすべし ・Twitterのニュース欄やトレンド、スペース機能を大いにパクッていくべきだ。Twitterは良くも悪くも「表に出ない情報と噂の共有」に大きな社会的価値があった。それを提供出来なければ、Threadsは、Twitterに変わる社会インフラ足りえないだろう 以上
